### 2. Import the Ontology
- Select your new repository from the dropdown
- Go to **Import → RDF → Import RDF text**
- Copy and paste the entire TTL file above
- Set **Base IRI**: `https://pgo.example.org/ontology#`
- Set **Context (Named graph)**: `https://pgo.example.org/ontology`
- Click **Import**

### 3. Verify Import
- Go to **Explore → Graphs overview**
- You should see your ontology graph
- Click on it to see ~20 classes and ~30 properties

### 4. Add Sample Data
Create a file `sample-data.ttl`:

```turtle
